":"eda57baa3854b6574179afc34b38044283c5961f","tid":1695944,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"網上傳出一條何君堯執葉律師於街站受狂徒襲擊的超清晰片段。<br />\n<br />\n由狂徒與何律師閒聊、送花、行兇過程、被制服的過程，無比清楚。不禁令人擔心何律師的傷勢，以及佩服拍片人的清閒。<br />\n<br />\n試問誰會如此清閒於街站拍片，內容起初還是兩個無聊人在談天？相信拍片人本應是想從早拍到晚，紀錄一下何律師辛勤耕耘社區的影像。只不過剛好巧合地又拍到了整個行兇過程罷了。<br />\n<br />\n請問，這部容量大、拍片清、電量高的電話在哪兒可以買到呢？<br />\n<br />\n最後，相信何律師可以早日康復，始終做戲不用那麼真。"},{"pid":"90134122d0e98c37eb771d79f3cd7ed8f76d6af4","tid":1695944,"uid":129704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"假<br />\n完"},{"pid":"825c1d14c83f6cf2bcb211b8d2e09e2f94c32063","tid":1695944,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d751117b85d4bb15d8cfcabe3788c3380ee1fac0","tid":1695944,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2236ca2b70aef6aa240e11dd73e33864ac14f96","tid":1695944,"uid":196397,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:18:57.000Z","msg":"渣機條友冷靜到一個點 好似知道之後會發生咩事 正常人都唔會啦 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"全程定到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到人插完都繼續影全程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"係 勁可疑 正常一定嚇一嚇"},{"pid":"9fa83f980512a4c3b7096639ed62dce4dc3b4916","tid":1695944,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6600e11aa0a3fc53c400204f711724ff38832453","tid":1695944,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1Q1Xjm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih